Immediate Former Agriculture Cabinet Secretary Mwangi Kiunjuri Has Decried What He Says Is Selective Application Of The Law With Bias On People Perceived To Be Against A Certain Political Order. Kiunjuri, A DP William Ruto Ally Was Fired From The Cabinet Last Month And Now Says His Stand On Development Issues In Central Kenya Must Have Rubbed The President And His Allies The Wrong Way. Kiunjuri Spoke At Fundraiser In PCEA Nanyuki.